name: Hide behind Wall [Exhibitionism]
description:
This Lora will help to generate pictures with the concept of a person standing in front of a wall, that covers half of the picture and a street/ other place in the background.

The model will tend to give (bottomless) nude characters if not further specified, but the concept is also appliable on clothed characters.


This Model can be used for SFW Concepts, but it will tend to produce NSFW

Main Trigger word is: hiding
But exhibitionism, public_indency and blushing can support the concept


It will generate most likely a street as background, but you can prompt other things, and it seems to work fine. I tested with school, hallway for example
You can also try different concept of the wall like "bus stop" for example, but this can lead to pictures not following the concept.

I recommend to use weights between 0.7 and 1. It all gave me decent results, but the best I got was with 0.8


This is the first LoRA I created, so I'm grateful for every feedback - positive or negative
You can support me on Kofi if you like

meta.prompt: ((best quality)), ((masterpiece)), (detailed), (cute, nerdy, round glasses, red hair, braids, freckles),  hiding, public_indecency, blush, exhibionism, school uniform, bus stop, <lora:hiding_behind_wall-07:0.8><hypernet:anime:1>
